# Canonicalize commit author identity. `git log`, `git shortlog -sn`, and
# GitHub's contributor display all consult this file to fold author
# variants into one canonical entry. The underlying commit objects are
# unchanged — this only affects how identity is presented.
#
# Format: <canonical-name> <canonical-email> <historic-name> <historic-email>
# (Lines without an old-name section match by email only.)

